 1.\nThis means its sort of .","created":"2024-06-28T22:58","updated":"2024-07-07T23:05","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:crypto:naptime:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/crypto/without-a-trace","title":"","description":"We are allowed to change the 5 cells of a 5 by 5 diagonal matrix.","created":"2024-06-28T22:58","updated":"2024-07-07T23:05","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:crypto:without-a-trace:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/crypto/x-marked-the-spot","title":"","description":"We observe that the flag is encrypted with XOR with a cycling key of length 8.\nAnd since we already know 8 characters of the flag (which happens to be length 48), we can determine the key by cipher ^ plain = key.","created":"2024-06-28T22:58","updated":"2024-07-07T23:05","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:crypto:X Marked the Spot:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf","title":"UIUCTF 2024","description":"#28 7489 points.","created":"2024-06-28T22:58","updated":"2024-07-07T22:22","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/misc/astea","title":"","description":"We are not allowed to use the following expressions in python: assign, call, import, import from, binary operation (+-/ etc).","created":"2024-06-29T00:39","updated":"2024-07-07T23:05","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:misc:astea:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/misc","title":"","description":"Very hard challenges, would love if there was more time for me to learn assembly.","created":"2024-06-28T22:58","updated":"2024-06-30T21:00","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:misc:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/misc/picoify","title":"Picoify","description":"FAILED TO SOLVE","created":"2024-06-30T20:40","updated":"2024-07-07T23:06","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:misc:Picoify.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/web/fare-evasion","title":"","description":"","created":"2024-06-28T20:52","updated":"2024-07-07T23:06","_id":"content:ctf:2024-uiuctf:web:fare-evasion:index.md"},{"_path":"/ctf/2024-uiuctf/web/handout","title"